q
BT 1 0 0 1 0 51 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (This paper identifies and formalizes the ) Tj /F2 9 Tf (Coherence Trap) Tj /F1 9 Tf (: a dynamical regime in which high average coherence masks) Tj T* (deterministic collapse. The mechanism is oscillatory coherence that periodically passes through zero, and it is the) Tj T* (zero-crossings -- not the mean -- that determine survival. We connect this phenomenon to the Caldeira-Leggett model of) Tj T* (structured baths, draw analogies to addiction in biological systems and RLHF alignment failure in artificial intelligence, and) Tj T* (provide diagnostic criteria for distinguishing genuine coherence from trapped coherence.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
